title: Mitchell saddles first winner in eight years
text: Mitchell saddles first winner in eight years Thursday, 22 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) PHILIP MITCHELL, famous for his American exploits with dirt lover Running Stag, enjoyed another important success at Kempton on Wednesday evening when Choral Clan became the trainer's first winner in eight years.
